text: the messed up missing cubbies we seen on joel’s workshop was due to the fact that those other templates hadn’t had an unassigned cubby template setup yet. so the cubbies that would have had that unassigned template assigned to them had nothing, so the space wasnt being used so the dom collapsed, or errored when it hit the unassigned ones, and since his started with an unassigned spot it showed nothing. where as the one i had made had complete assignment of users except that last spot, so was unseen as an issue. easy fix, just setup the template with the unassigned template. done
